  "code": "stateDiagram-v2\n    [Infra_IngressController] --> New : Process created\n    New --> Ready : Admit (Infra_LoadBalancer)\n    Ready --> Running : Dispatch (Infra_RedisCache)\n    Running --> Waiting : I/O or event wait\n    Running --> Ready : Interrupt (Infra_WorkerNode)\n    Running --> Terminated : Exit (Infra_IngressController)\n    \n    Waiting --> Ready : I/O completed\n    Waiting --> Suspended_Wait : Swap out (Infra_LoadBalancer)\n    Suspended_Wait --> Suspended_Ready : I/O completed\n    Suspended_Ready --> Ready : Swap in (Infra_EtcdCluster)\n    \n    Terminated --> [Infra_IngressController]",
